result.name: Dai Kee

reviews.text: Noodle Restaurant focusing on Rice Noodle. Funny Texture comparing other restaurant on the market.
tried 5 types of dessert pastry, ok, not very sweet

A very local eatery specializing on a kind of rice noodle which is more thick with some chewy characteristics.  Can be combined with a large range of meat and vegetables and one bowl is good and balance for a meal, and cost some only $30+ so very high CP value.  Also the shop serves a lot of very traditional snacks and sweets, all freshly made and thus a very interesting place to enjoy a meal or some snacks.  Basic deco but clean and well attended.
Great and very special and traditional food (Lai noodles). A lot of local snacks for your taking away as well.

It's just alright for me in the noodles.

Dessert drinks are better.

result.name: 大記攦粉

reviews.text: 地方细'食物都幾好、可以一試。

環景唔算太大，服務好有禮！
食物唔錯，糕點一流🖒
店舖不是太大，各種攦粉都很有水準，亦有很多榚品亦很受市民歡迎！
不過不失，可以一試。
味道還好, 可惜開在内街, 人客不容易找
